collab OrderRoutingExample

(s) Start
    => RouteOrder

<x> RouteOrder
  order.amount > 10000 => HighValueReview
  customer.tier = "gold" => AutoApprove
  =>d ManualReview

[] HighValueReview
    => MergeDone
[] AutoApprove
    => MergeDone
[] ManualReview
    => MergeDone
<> MergeDone
    => Done
(e) Done
